{"tid":2130241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實醫護人員成撚日擦光環，都幾撚嘔心","createTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T06:34:19.000Z","uid":123306,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c3c439b22bf6245537d41486727171c60cd17d3e","tid":2130241,"uid":123306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"政府唔封關係仆街，但醫護凍薪其實好合理。講真出面咩環境，行行都減薪、放無薪假，有份高薪又穩定既工，仲想點?  唔好忘記，好多護士都係護校畢業，拎住十幾分做專業人士，都真係咪笑人地讀毅進。"},{"pid":"ea933ca96a9856950094293929abb3d247497bc6","tid":2130241,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"你又啱, 份份工都係咁架啦<br />\n唔滿意咪辭職囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33082eeced08050e7cfc7c6aca5e281759cb694c","tid":2130241,"uid":179292,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c3c439b22bf6245537d41486727171c60cd17d3e","tid":2130241,"uid":123306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"政府唔封關係仆街，但醫護凍薪其實好合理。講真出面咩環境，行行都減薪、放無薪假，有份高薪又穩定既工，仲想點?  唔好忘記，好多護士都係護校畢業，拎住十幾分做專業人士，都真係咪笑人地讀毅進。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:09:14.000Z","msg":"如果醫護凍薪合理，咁特首、高官、警察同樣都應該凍薪，因為醫護搵條命去搏，後面個D ，我唔講，大家都心知佢哋既工作態度。"},{"pid":"98f7ed070df731ac55b6786e2e8b27c20a080806","tid":2130241,"uid":200083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"擦你老母"},{"pid":"25c7c27432776fa647ab4412485ee44b92881dda","tid":2130241,"uid":123306,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:11:56.000Z","msg":"再講，成撚日係度製造恐慌。你有醫護既專業，就有知識同責任向公眾解釋肺炎既死亡率、醫治既方法、康復既過程等，而唔係同政府口徑一致，瘋狂叫人口罩同唔好出街。醫護人員咁撚大個道德光環，同政府既限聚令、限堂食措施捆綁埋一齊，根本就係合力製造恐慌，加強政府嘅維穩功能"},{"pid":"5e2508ecf50739d4fa2fbba597c695d80a2d912d","tid":2130241,"uid":127067,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"靜左幾日，又夠鐘抄返熱去批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"836945ac3dcc98c2ea001c002256ebef1945d44e","tid":2130241,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P3wCrzq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP3wCrzq.jpg&h=20b564d1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BhMSfsM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBhMSfsM.jpg&h=4946df97&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3Bfder.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3Bfder.png&h=de5a5f7b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9394985c54ae932c1beef066474c9fcbde884005","tid":2130241,"uid":123306,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:19:17.000Z","msg":"再講護士既編更。<br />\nA - 早更，7am - 3pm <br />\nP - 中更，2:30pm - 10:30pm <br />\nNight - 通宵更，10pm - 翌日7am <br />\n<br />\n一更得7至8個鐘，當你OT埋，9個鐘好未? 都只不過等於出面一份私人工，唔洗OT，正常既office hour。仲要唔洗攞野返屋企做，一年25大假。<br />\n<br />\n成日話偉大，望下啲返工時間幾短先得架!"},{"pid":"0ea8ef1a572f98cd6afb4667886fa485089c3214","tid":2130241,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea933ca96a9856950094293929abb3d247497bc6","tid":2130241,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"你又啱, 份份工都係咁架啦<br />\n唔滿意咪辭職囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:20:31.000Z","msg":"我有個表姐做護士頂唔順 辭咗職去賣生果<br />\n所以唔好話轉唔到工定點樣 係睇你有冇決心"},{"pid":"e03965996fbf32b862eed9980e2385eb55bced2c","tid":2130241,"uid":198040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:20:33.000Z","msg":"Blocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1860a2172dff94f070ea69dcd86e57c9c66c0b61","tid":2130241,"uid":76514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"擦乜撚 要擦吓個環先夠光？"},{"pid":"e7eab5748a4fe47f022250309c48f1f13a7435ae","tid":2130241,"uid":359419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime